this young fellow is starved.

11:52.040 --> 11:53.580
Oh, I made these myself.

11:53.580 --> 11:54.660
Oh, don't apologize, Al.

11:54.660 --> 11:55.660
I'll eat anything,
you know.

11:55.660 --> 11:58.630
Oh, yeah, uh,
how about... liver?

11:58.630 --> 12:00.300
Oh, well,
this is good, Fonz.

12:00.300 --> 12:01.640
